                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 159</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The first of the three conversations between Secretary of State <persName
                        corresp="#p_ADG1">Acheson</persName> and Foreign Minister <persName
                        corresp="#p_SR1">Schuman</persName> took place on March 29 and was concerned
                    exclusively with problems raised at the Four-Power Exploratory Talks then taking
                    place in Paris. For minutes of this first meeting, see <ref
                        target="frus1951v03p1#pg_1112">volume III, Part 1, page 1112</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
